## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let image=new Image();
image.onload=function(){
  resolve(image)
}
image.onerror=function(){
  reject(new Error('图片加载失败'+src+'路径错误'))
}
image.src=src
